>> title: Rune's Mom's Chocolate Mousse
>> description:  We always had this at New Year's or for special celebrations
>> date: 2025-03-23

In #blender{} add @semi sweet chocolate chips{1.5%cup}, @eggs{2}, @rum or Grand Marnier{1%shot}, and scalded @half and half{1.5%cup}.

Blend until chips are melted and mixed well.

Immediately pour into cups or wine glasses. Cover with plastic wrap and refrigerate.

Chill overnight.

Serve with @whipped cream{} on top (can dust with cinnamon if desired)